data.description: WOW! This gorgeous, modern, spacious home has absolutely everything you're looking for and more! With five bedrooms, an open kitchen, vaulted ceilings, and a great layout, this beauty has all the space you'll need! The first thing you'll notice when you pull up to your new home is the outstanding curb appeal. Entering the home you'll find tons of windows and those high vaulted ceilings that lend to a bright, airy feel. Your fully open kitchen has granite counters, an eating bar island, beautiful tile backsplash, stainless appliances, and stylish cabinetry, PLUS a walk-in pantry! The adjoining dining area is situated right in front of a bay window with lovely views into your backyard. You will love your master suite that has a separate soaking tub and shower, plus a dual vanity with granite counters. The other bedrooms are just as spacious and bright. In the view-out basement you'll find a huge recreation room with a set of built-in shelves for an entertainment center, plus a wet bar. The basement also features two more bedrooms and a bathroom. And check out your new backyard! Situated on a nearly quarter-acre lot, there is a gigantic deck, a fully-fenced yard, a covered patio area, and so much space for the kids or dogs to run around in! It's truly an oasis within the city. This home has so much space, stylish and modern paint and finishes, and it's conveniently located  close to highways and shopping while still feeling tucked away. As a bonus, this community has access to a swimming pool and other neighborhood amenities! A house this beautiful and packed with features will not last long so call today to schedule your private showing before it's gone!
